<MainLayout title="About Sports Jam">
  <section class="py-16 current-highlight">
    <div class="container px-4 mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap mb-32 mt-14 -mx-8">
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 px-8">
          <img
            class="rounded-3xl w-full mb-8"
            src="https://static.shuffle.dev/uploads/files/9f/9f7be124245360ff3df9b74a86a83b1f67022b7a/about-us-image.jpg"
            alt=""
          />
        </div>
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 px-8">
          <Badge class="mb-4">ABOUT US</Badge>
          <h1
            class="font-heading text-5xl mb-10 xs:text-6xl md:text-8xl xl:text-10xl font-bold text-gray-900"
          >
            We Live To <span class="font-serif italic">Move</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600 leading-9 text-lg">
            Sports Jam was born out of Jam's passion for sports. We officially
            launched Sports Jam with a free 'Come and Try Sports Day' for
            children aged 6 to 12 on October 13, 2018, coinciding with what
            would have been Jam's 11th birthday, held at 185 Old Northern Rd,
            Albany Creek, Queensland.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-9">
            Initially, our focus was on promoting the 'Come and Try Sports Day'
            to schools and communities, offering kids the opportunity to
            experience multiple sports in one venue.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-10 leading-9">
            However, as our community has grown, we've expanded our offerings
            beyond this event. Moving forward, we are planning to introduce
            sports clinics, dance classes, and more, embracing a holistic
            approach to promoting the spirit of movement.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
